{"type":"article","id":15987,"title":"來來來！小本本拿出來，英國國會收集黑警罪證啦！！！","uid":31531,"topics":[4710,2248,3160,2573],"contents":"英國國會「跨黨派國會香港小組」（All-Party Parliamentary Group Hong Kong）今日（10日）宣布調查香港警察打壓港人人權狀況，調查結果將提交英國政府。小組現時開始搜集證據，呼籲各方人士提供。<br>\n<br>\n小組正在展開首次國會調查，將就香港警察自「反送中」運動以來，涉嫌針對「人道支援人員」及「提供支援工作相關器材的人員」，尤其是醫護人員所作的行動，調查有否違反國際人權法。<br>\n<br>\n「跨黨派國會香港小組」呼籲，各界人士若有相關證據，可於官方網站提交，截止日期為 4 月 7 日。及後小組將邀請個別提供證據人士及團體親身作供，收集證供後撰寫報告呈交英國政府，並提出建議。<br>\n<br>\n全文：<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/r-%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25B7%25A8%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%25B3%25A8%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25B0%258F%25E7%25B5%2584%25E1%2585%25A0%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E5%25B8%2583-%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%25A3%2593%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A%25E7%258B%2580%25E6%25B3%2581-%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E6%258F%2590%25E4%25BE%259B%25E8%25AD%2589%25E6%2593%259A/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/r-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%83%E8%B7%A8%E9%BB%A8%E6%B4%BE%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%B0%8F%E7%B5%84%E1%85%A0%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83-%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E6%89%93%E5%A3%93%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E7%8B%80%E6%B3%81-%E7%B1%B2%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E8%AD%89%E6%93%9A/</a><br>\n<br>\nCredit:&nbsp;https://lihkg.com/thread/1918727/page/1<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/It7aOGJ.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/It7aOGJ.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/It7aOGJ.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\nIns: chengwaihok<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/lOwRHYP.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/lOwRHYP.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/lOwRHYP.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/Ae1nRjE.jpg\